Install intellij and intellij-jdk (aur) and actual jdk.

Start intellij and select which JDK for it to boot from by doing

    - Ctrl+Shift+A and type "Switch IDE Boot JDK" and select intellij-jdk

Info from here: https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206544879-Selecting-the-JDK-version-the-IDE-will-run-under
